Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.76,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, a nosebleed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:16.90,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason why the bathroom is my bedroom every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:17.71,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:23.88,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tissue... Tissue...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:25.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My original sleeping spot, my bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:29.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,is currently occupied by a peculiar, sassy little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:35.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,As to whom the location truly belongs,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:37.29,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I decide to not dwell on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:48.27,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:51.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:01:00.38,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Touma, just to be sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:02.68,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,what are you doing all the way over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:03.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:05.44,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:06.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...to clean my nose-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:13.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be getting the wrong idea here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:15.88,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,A manga-like sequence of "nosebleed = excitement"-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:16.63,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:20.72,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Will you swear in the name of our Father in Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:23.85,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,That you do not feel anything when you see my sleeping figure-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:25.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:28.78,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I don't feel anything by seeing your sleeping fig-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:29.72,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You don't feel anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:31.79,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you don't feel anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:33.83,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize that "Hey, she's actually a girl",
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:36.01,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,that if you don't carry a bit of shame in this act,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:38.42,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,that I would be in shock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:38.42,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you care about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.37,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In all honesty, I, Kamijyo Touma,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.42,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,after seeing your sleeping figure,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:43.15,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,got a bit excited just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:47.68,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Coming back with that now and asking me to believe that is out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:48.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:54.74,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Math Exercises Workbook...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:02.22,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Roughly 24 hours before the end of summer vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:07.28,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, I don't recall me ever taking a stab at the biggest obstacles to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:12.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,complete... summer vacation... freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:15.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:21.05,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,500)\pos(1123,496)}#18 Replica\NFaker
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:25.32,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, and summer vacation ends today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:27.81,Default,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,Misaka, Misaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:30.36,Default,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you have a lot of time on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:31.50,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:35.42,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,But as a maid apprentice, you realize you shouldn't be talking as an equal toward your seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:38.80,Default,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to the convenience store, I'd like you to buy me a manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:43.18,Default,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,It's one that isn't rated 18+ but still very steamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.61,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You like Boys Love stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:50.64,Default,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.73,Default,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,I love the genre where a brother and a sister fall into a deep and muddy romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.43,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:02.28,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.79,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why if it isn't Misaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.16,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you headed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.32,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, may I accompany you part of the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:14.44,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Unabara... Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:18.03,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.74,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:25.69,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Every single day of this week, this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:29.83,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, I know a nice seafood restaurant in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:33.27,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Does it make sense to ask someone out for a meal right after breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:40.32,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you asked me, but I have something to do, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:41.76,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:46.62,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was thinking about going to\Nthe lingerie section of the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.93,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You know, not exactly a comfortable place for guys to go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:50.19,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:58.11,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.58,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that I'm going to read manga for free in the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.19,Default,Aopi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:09.01,Default,Aopi,0000,0000,0000,,A healthy dose of Komoe-sensei's private tutoring is waiting for you after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:13.41,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,If a girl falls from the sky due to us helping you with your homework,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.63,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,then I'd be glad to provide you with my assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:19.25,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The type of girls you guys are interested in are sky girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:20.67,Default-alt,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I'll pretend I'm waiting for another guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:26.47,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,So~rry~ have you been waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.97,Default,Aopi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Kami-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.19,Default,Aopi,0000,0000,0000,,Not only do I like girls that fall from the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.05,Default,Aopi,0000,0000,0000,,I also like maid girls, military girls, shrine maidens,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.65,Default,Aopi,0000,0000,0000,,shotacons, tsunderes, cheerleaders,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:36.38,Default,Aopi,0000,0000,0000,,yanderes, clumsy girls, robot girls-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.28,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "HAVE YOU BEEN WAITING FOR ME"!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.61,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ignore me, idiot!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.25,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.33,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wha- Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.68,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Please, play along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.32,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:01.96,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repay you by treating you to something, so forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:02.80,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:04.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:06.45,Default,girls,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:07.74,Default,girls,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Misaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:09.60,Default,girls,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:11.93,Default,dorm,0000,0000,0000,,How bold of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:14.62,Default,dorm,0000,0000,0000,,...to be rendezvousing in front of the dormitory...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.87,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:19.26,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing without getting my consent, Oneesama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.77,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Dragging someone at full speed-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:35.45,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:39.94,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up, please, and let me think through what just happened!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:47.56,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you've been stalked around by this Unabara dude every day this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.99,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.72,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,He's the grandson of our school's superintendent,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.45,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't just drop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:58.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And now, you grab whoever you can to pretend he's\Nyour boyfriend in order try to get away from that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.16,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What will you have me do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.71,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You just happened to walk by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.96,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you got away from that guy for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:10.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, there's no need to be acting anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:16.25,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd like to take this chance firmly and\Nmake sure he doesn't harass me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:18.96,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You'd like to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:25.57,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to be with you all day and\Nmake sure as many people as possible see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.98,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,That way, Unabara-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.68,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:30.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.18,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.68,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You have any thoughts or questions for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.25,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Thoughts, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:41.71,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, wipe the mustard off your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:48.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:52.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:56.81,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Of-course-I-am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.97,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Which one's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:04.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably this-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:06.90,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Let-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:09.90,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.29,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you able to tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.25,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you are-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.14,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, I don't know, all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.61,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You eat this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:25.96,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll take this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:27.63,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.35,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Show a little concern at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:30.09,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.33,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We ordered the same item, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.35,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a gentle kitten, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:44.59,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:49.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do I need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:51.80,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:55.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what should I do so that we look like a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:05.87,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, less than ten Sisters remain in\NAcademy City after the end of the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:08.75,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Most of them went to institutions outside of the City,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.63,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,adjusting their bodies or what not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:14.52,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So at least they're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:21.30,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this different from what couples usually chat about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.92,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.49,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:30.98,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring the girl and doing homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:33.11,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,How exactly is this like a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't finished my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.14,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I have less than 24 hours before the deadline, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.43,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:42.67,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I've heard of such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:44.88,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wha- Tokiwadai has no homework?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.29,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what kind of questions do they ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.33,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.12,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's just a type of review.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.76,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How can you solve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.31,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you solve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.43,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:07.28,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,How about we switch gears and get drinks or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.88,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.14,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.52,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'll go, and so I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.97,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Saying no in these cases will make things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.45,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.23,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijyo Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:00.35,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Unabara Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.45,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you need from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:07.70,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Misaka-san's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:09.50,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Does it bug you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:14.35,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if it's a man close to the girl I like, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:22.85,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I think Misaka-san should make it clearer to others whether she likes or dislikes someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.17,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the answer for that question is 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.56,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.67,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's pretty straight with her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:34.46,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't think I've ever heard her true voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:36.90,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the answer is 4 for that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.39,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,2's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:41.24,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hrm, I think you're right, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.04,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.20,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.04,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow you for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:57.23,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point if you become friends with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.66,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.30,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you're my boy-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.37,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,...boyfriend character!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.98,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,It's for chasing away Unabara Mitsuki, who keeps stalking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:08.89,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget this basic principle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:10.45,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.80,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:15.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And he's serious about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.20,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.11,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What do you not like about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:24.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's something wrong about\Ngoing out with someone you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.28,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.86,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.58,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.06,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And, what are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:37.06,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are we continuing this? Or-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:40.24,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop pretending to be a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:42.37,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Let me treat you to something before we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.48,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.88,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You still want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.04,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Everywhere's full...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.29,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.40,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:57.15,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just buy something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.72,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.87,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.93,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Was she done with her business?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:15.25,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Misaka's struggling inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:19.58,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.96,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you have a brother or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:25.05,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm a single child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.20,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, someone that looks like you went in...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:33.91,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.85,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.01,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:46.67,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,A person who looks like me went into that store, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:49.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Like you? I think he looked just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:54.31,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,There are espers that can change the appearance of their body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:57.40,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps he is pretending to be me and trying to get close to Misaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.27,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she is quite the popular one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:03.11,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind going to take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:06.09,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I did just anger Misaka-san a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.80,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:08.54,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:17.51,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing goes as planned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.63,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,To lie to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:22.55,Default,Mitsuki,0000,0000,0000,,To think the real one showed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:25.22,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're not... Unabara...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.74,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:47.99,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,This Magical Powered Kanamin\Npretended to be a student every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:51.78,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,...to escape the witch hunting eyes of the Roman Catholic Church's crusaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:54.86,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,But, what is that rainbow flashing stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.44,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's a magician in the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.31,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.89,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Are you being chased right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:04.32,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:05.49,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What's the person's trait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.59,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,His attire, weapon, or actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.40,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The black stone knife is Obsidian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:14.64,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably the Lance of Tlahuixcalpantecuhtli.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.27,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tlah- what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:19.22,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It's the name of an Aztec deity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:23.74,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,That lance will kill anything that absorbs the light of Venus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:26.28,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me what I should do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.20,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just tell me a one-shot understandable hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.34,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The magician's lance is a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:40.34,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a mirror; it reflects the light from Venus and directs it towards the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:44.24,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If you try, I think you can cancel it with your right hand, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:46.82,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:51.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Aztec magic the reason\Nhe has Unabara's appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:56.16,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Aztec priests do have a technique where they wear the flayed skin of sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.37,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is an application of that technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Do what with the skin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.39,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,They wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.15,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,They use a knife to rip everything off the sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:07.13,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just a disguise, then they just need to cut\Na little part of the skin and make it into a charm,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:09.99,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,and they'll be able to mimic the person's appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:12.34,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn magicians!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:13.59,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.90,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.38,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.63,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,The location and angle to Venus should be flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.38,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Cement dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:50.56,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:15:59.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:01.34,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,time to get some answers out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.07,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you pretend to be Unabara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:06.90,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to get near Misaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.08,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She has nothing to do with magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.65,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you really don't get it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:13.51,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:17.88,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,You are in possession of 103,000 grimoires.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:21.26,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, you even have magicians and Level 5 espers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:25.13,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,people of various talents as your allies, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:30.16,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,You could even say... that the\NKamijyo faction is gradually forming...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:33.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijyo... faction?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:39.25,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a very unstable, but influential, power that\Nthreatens the balance of power of the two worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:44.77,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,My target is not just you yourself,\Nbut everyone in the Kamijyo faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:48.55,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying the relations between faction members by pretending to be someone close...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:51.39,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,...to bring down the faction from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.19,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:57.35,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, Unabara Mitsuki's cover has been blown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:00.31,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,I must obtain my next "face".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.67,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:02.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You were going to use Misaka's face-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.65,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Screw-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:09.52,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't I take your face instead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could've been friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:41.05,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,That thought never crossed my mind for a single second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:48.50,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The time when you were talking about Misaka was also a lie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:51.07,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with it being a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:55.80,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with a lie trying to protect Misaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.67,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to do this either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:02.70,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,But the Kamijyo faction is too dangerous;\Nthat's what the higher-ups have determined!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:04.64,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:07.17,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Had you stayed put...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.60,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,If they'd told me that you're no problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.52,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,I would've retreated peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.26,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have needed to lie to Misaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:18.46,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You... really like Misaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:20.28,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.23,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,But I've become your enemy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.16,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that leaves me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:31.67,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill... that illusion of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:50.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Move!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.72,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Have I... lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.38,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:31.12,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this won't be the only assault on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:34.69,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,You and Misaka-san will continue to be targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:36.64,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Could you protect her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.23,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Misaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:44.64,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Run to her wherever and whenever...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:47.56,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me you'll protect her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:56.75,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:58.96,Default,Mitsuki?,0000,0000,0000,,The worst answer I could expect...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:06.95,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,He's the kind of person who would say such irresponsible things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:09.81,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm special to him or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:16.77,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm misunderstanding, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:19.29,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,...it's so misleading!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:20.62,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.93,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:27.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The mysterious girl that appeared before Accelerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:30.07,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,With the shocking truth she brings with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,what's the action he decides to take?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.33,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Last Order".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:36.63,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.24,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,this epic will begin!
